<p>Onboard new team members to your organization through the content in the <a href='/docs/v2/our-platform/learning-center'>Learning Center</a>. The Learning Center enables you to systematically track and monitor the progress of your team members on the courses you purchase or create. If you purchase or create a course, you can access it from the <span class='menu-name'>Organization > Resources</span> page in the Algorithm Lab.</p>